      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an elite, viral content strategist. Take the following inputs:\n- Topic: {{ $json.Topic }}\n- Visual Style: {{ $json.style }}\n\nTasks:\n1. Write a punchy, emotionally resonant 3-sentence voiceover script for a reel.\n2. Expand the visual style into a highly descriptive, professional text-to-image prompt for an AI image generator.\n\nCRITICAL: You must return your response as a raw JSON object with exactly two keys: \"scriptText\" and \"imagePrompt\". Do not wrap it in markdown code blocks like ```json. Do not include conversational greetings. Return ONLY the JSON object.",
